transcripts: So this is the Mo an adjustable curved shower rod from bed bath and beyond. This adjustable curved shower rod allows you to easily transform the look of your bathroom without the cost of a pricey remodel the shower rod conveniently adjusts from 54 inches up to 72 inches because of the unique curved shower rod feel experienced 7 and 1/2 inches of more elbow room in the shower when the rod is expanded to full length. This shower rod is constructed of quality stainless steel and comes in three stylish finishes chrome old-world bronze and brushed nickel. This Mo an adjustable curved shower rod is easy to install and all mounting hardware is included and the mounting posts pivot 180 degrees for a flexible installation. The Mo an adjustable curved shower rod available online or at a bed bath and beyond near you.
